    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In preferences <strong>Java -> Code Style -> Formatter</strong>, edit the profile. Under the <strong>Line Wrapping</strong> tab is the primary option for line width (Maximum line width:). In the <strong>Comments</strong> tab you have a separate option <em>Maximum line width for comments:</em>, which will also need to be changed to affect comment wrapping.</p>\n\n<p>You will need to make your own profile to make these changes in if you using one of the <code>[Built-in]</code> ones. Just click \"New...\" on the formatter preferences page.</p>\n"
