    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Preferences -> Java -> Code Style -> Formatter  / \"Edit...\"</p>\n\n<p>Tabs: \"Line wrapping\" , \"Comments\"</p>\n\n<p>Field: \"Maximum line width\" </p>\n\n<p>Set both to make comments have the same length too.\nYou might need to create a new profile if you don't have one already.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3658649,
      "reputation" : 1601,
