    "question_id" : 3697287,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Line length formatter setup is blocked for annotations (Eclipse Photon checked). Therefore it is needed in <em>Line Wrapping -> Wrapping settings -> Annotations</em>. Setup line wrapping as appropriate for you. There is couple of possibilities, e.q. <em>Enable wrap when necessary</em> to use first icon list.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/4v5Ra.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/4v5Ra.png\" alt=\" \"></a></p>\n"
  } ],
